description:
This is a 25 minute workout called 'Advanced Guided Breathing For Maximum Focus' from the channel Kitaro Waga.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Advanced and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Advanced and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.
